NT||cp|8|AT|^B@2^Y@3^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|First the bidding. Anna probably has a more descriptive bid than 2N. That is 2H which is a reverse. That way she shows both her shape (5+ clubs and 4 hearts) and points (16+). As it turns out we end up in 3N anyway. Let me briefly go over the way to respond to the 3D new minor forcing bid. My 3D bid guarantees that I have 5 spades. I may or may not have 4 hearts. The reason being with 4 hearts and 4 spades I would have bid 1H, so I must have 5 spades in order to do new minor forcing.|
