NT||cp|8|AT|^B@2^Y@3^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Further, notice that Anna's 2N bid, although not best with her hand, does not deny 4 hearts (for example were she 2-4-3-4) she has a clear 2N bid. So, remember the auction 1 minor - 1H or 1S - 2N does not deny a 4 card major. It simply shows a balanced 18-19.|
